2014-06-15  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	Version 2.2.10 released.

2014-05-26  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* tramp.texi (External methods): Remove "sftp".
	(GVFS based methods): Add "sftp".

2014-05-13  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* tramp.texi (Inline methods): Reinsert "plinkx".
	(External methods): Do not mention session names anymore.

