	* tramp.texi (Frequently Asked Questions): Mention HISTFILE
	setting in ~/.ssh/environment.

2014-04-25  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* trampinst.texi (Testing): Environment variable
	REMOTE_ALLOW_PASSWORD not needed anymore.

2014-04-24  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* trampinst.texi (Testing): The test suite uses a mock-up connection.

2014-03-24  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* tramp.texi (Customizing Completion, External packages, Issues):
	Use @dots{}.
	(Frequently Asked Questions): Add fish shell settings.
	(Inline methods): Recommend sharing ssh connections for "plink".
	Remove "plinkx".
	(External methods): Merge "pscp" and "psftp" descriptions.
	Recommend sharing ssh connections.

2014-03-13  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* tramp.texi (Inline methods): Remove restriction on "telnet".
	(External methods): Add "nc" method.

