	* tramp.texi: Add @documentencoding.

2014-01-12  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* tramp.texi (all): Doc fix according to GNU Coding Standards.
	Use "file name" instead of "filename" or "path".  Use "host"
	instead of "machine".

