	(Remote shell setup): Replace literal NUL character by \0.

2012-12-22  Paul Eggert  <eggert@cs.ucla.edu>

	* tramp.texi: Hyphen and dash fixes in texinfo files.

2012-12-21  Glenn Morris  <rgm@gnu.org>

	* tramp.texi: Do not mention buying copies from the FSF, which
	does not publish these manuals.

2012-12-14  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* tramp.texi (External methods): Move `adb' method here.

2012-12-05  Paul Eggert  <eggert@cs.ucla.edu>

	* tramp.texi: Fix minor whitespace issues after "." in manual.

	Be more systematic about using "@." (not ".") at end of sentence that
	ends in a capital letter, and about appending "@:" after non-ends of
	sentences that end in a lower case letter followed by "." followed by
	whitespace.  Omit unnecessary use of "@:" and "@.".  Similarly for "?"
	and "!".  Be more consistent about putting a comma after "i.e." and
	"e.g."; this is the typical American style and it's easier to code in
	Texinfo.

2012-12-02  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* .gitignore: Add file.

	* tramp.texi (Top, Obtaining Tramp): Replace CVS by Git.

